      <title>阿达尼集团宣称拥有大量现金以缓解兴登堡引发的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/adani-group-touts-cash-pile-to-ease-hindenburg-fueled-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度企业集团阿达尼集团 (Adani Group) 表示，其拥有足够的现金来偿还 30 多个月的债务，此举旨在缓解人们对其流动性风险的担忧，因为该集团正在考虑为其旗舰部门筹集新一轮资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/adani-group-touts-cash-pile-to-ease-hindenburg-fueled-concerns</guid>
